Cell["SyntaxForm", "Subsubsection",ExpressionUUID->"5103c720-eb44-4338-a920-dead2436530e"],

Cell["\<\
After add the tooltip, the precedence of operator gets lost since the outer \
level is a tooltip box instead of dot box.

The option SyntaxForm is to specify the precedence manually.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"903c0d72-9755-4571-920f-f17d27f0f6f9"],

